[ACADEMIC PARTNER REVEAL: Bincang Psikologi]

Are you prepared to welcome our upcoming academic partner with enthusiasm? Get ready, as we introduce Bincang Psikologi. 

Recognizing the crucial need for our students to prioritize their mental health, this collaboration with Bincang Psikologi is a purposeful initiative. Through this partnership, we aim to provide valuable resources and expertise to enhance our students' grasp of mental well-being and address their specific challenges. Our commitment lies in fostering a supportive environment that emphasizes the comprehensive development and mental resilience of our students.

Prepare yourself for this amazing collaboration. Stay tuned for the big announcement!

[ ACADEMIC PARTNER REVEAL : HABITAT FOR HUMANITY ]

Are you ready to greet our next academic partner with excitement? Well, here they come—introducing Habitat for Humanity. 

Habitat for Humanity is set to collaborate with us in a meaningful philanthropic initiative! As a worldwide nonprofit housing organization, Habitat for Humanity dedicates its efforts to providing decent homes for individuals in need, operating both in the United States and over 70 other countries. Through this partnership, students will engage in social projects, fostering positive transformations and gaining hands-on experience in creating enduring impacts.

Can’t wait to creating impact with Habitat for Humanity? Get ready for the big reveal. Stay tuned for the exciting announcement!
